fh - Static variable in class GIS.GIS
The File Handler for Database and CSV interaction.
fileChooser() - Method in class GIS.filehandling.FileHandler
This method opens a filechooser dialog box; The file chooser validates that the selected file is a .csv, if true a file name and file path are displayed in the appropriate text-boxes; if false an error message is displayed.
FileHandler - Class in GIS.filehandling
Creates new form (FileHandler), serves as connection between user input and the file storage classes Database and CSV
